upgradeTo.description: Upgrades the contract to a new implementation.

upgradeToAndCall.description: Upgrades the contract to a new implementation and then calls a function on the new implementation with provided data.

implementation.description: Returns the address of the current implementation contract.

changeAdmin.description: Changes the admin address of the contract.

admin.description: Returns the address of the current admin.

constructor.description: Initializes the contract with the given implementation address.

fallback.description: Fallback function that allows the contract to receive ether.

AdminChanged.description: Emitted when the admin address is changed.

Upgraded.description: Emitted when the contract is upgraded to a new implementation.
